	   <tr><td colspan=2>Not sure on any time limit. Our guild has spanked him quite a few times now, and never had him despawn on us... one thing to note though.<br><br>Memblur is safe when you are on the way to the dragon. We have a chanter and a group or two just in charge of the gnome, while the rest push forward killing whatever's around. Mez him, punch him to wake him up when you want to move, memblur.<br><br>However... once he triggers the dragon do NOT memblur or mez him. You will still get loot, etc, but you cannot get flagged for the PoI factory.<br><br>Hope any of that helps.<br>&nbsp;<br>Razormaw Balefire<br>Monk of the 51st Flurry<br><br>Master Branaddar Balefire<br>Wizard of the 62nd Spire<br>Tholuxe Paells<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=286983" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=286983</a></td></tr>
